p It.  <br><br>This year, Ken has chosen to go all out with a theme that has special meaning to him – the Titanic.  Ken was seven years old when the wreckage of the Titanic was discovered, since then he has been fascinated by the story and the ship.  He wanted to share his passion with his customers, especially the kids, who love the Titanic as much as he does. 
